('The Walking Dead by Robert Kirkman', 'https://picsum.photos/536/354?random=124', 'Graphic novel series about survivors in a zombie apocalypse.', 'Published from 2003-2019, this graphic novel series by Robert Kirkman follows survivors in a zombie apocalypse. The series explores themes of survival, community, and what it means to remain human in extreme circumstances.'),
