('The Matrix by William Gibson', 'https://picsum.photos/536/354?random=435', 'Cyberpunk novella about artificial intelligence and reality.', 'Published in 1984, this cyberpunk novella explores the nature of artificial intelligence and virtual reality. The book examines themes of consciousness, technology, and the blurred lines between human and machine intelligence.'),
('Hyperion Cantos by Dan Simmons', 'https://picsum.photos/536/354?random=480', 'Science fiction series about pilgrims journey to mysterious planet Hyperion.', 'Published from 1989-1997, this science fiction series follows pilgrims traveling to the mysterious planet Hyperion to encounter the deadly Shrike. The series explores themes of artificial intelligence, time travel, religion, and the evolution of humanity across time and space.'),
