('The Culture Series by Iain M. Banks', 'https://picsum.photos/536/354?random=503', 'Science fiction series about post-scarcity utopian society.', 'Published from 1987-2012, this science fiction series explores the Culture, a post-scarcity utopian society of humanoids and artificial intelligences. The series explores themes of artificial intelligence, ethics, politics, and the nature of consciousness in an advanced civilization.');
